===Etymology 1===
Perhaps from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*mV-kum|t=pillow, block, bench, bedstead}}, and cognate with {{cog|my|ခုံ|t=raised block}}, {{cog|sit-jap|tɤmkɯm||pillow}} (STEDT). {{zh-ref|Zhang, Jacques, and Lai (2019)}} suggest that the {{m|och||t-}} preinitial in {{zh-ref|Baxter and Sagart's (2014)}} {{cog|och|-}} may be related to the Gyalrong indefinite possessive prefix, such as {{ncog|sit-jap|tɤ-}}, from {{ncog|sit-pro|*tV-}}.

STEDT also suggests {{och-l|椹|chopping block}} as a comparandum, but it seems to be difficult to reconcile.

